 Here’s episode 10 of the web series “Highway Girls“. “Highway Girls” is centred on a group of smart and clever high school teens in a supersonic race to live adult life irrespective of the consequences. It brings to light the state of the street for the nurture of the girl child. The series stars Ejike Metusela, Sharon Ifedi, Emmanuel Precious, Nwabueze Rachael, Gladys Benson, Chuks Chyke and other talented actors. Watch the video below:   The best Nigerian and African video content from around the web specially curated for YOU! 